data.description: This stunning Ohio City home has been completely renovated from top to bottom in recent years and offers a FULL FIFTEEN YEAR TAX ABATEMENT! Qualifying and registered for 2023 tax year, the tax abatement will run through tax year 2038! The home lives large with 4 bedrooms, 3 full and 1 half bath. Every room in this home boasts high end design and finish work. The home features 2 fireplaces, one in the family room and one in the massive, primary suite. The backyard was recently completed with a large paver patio and astro turf complete with neutralizer to keep clean after pets. Call today for your personal tour and take advantage of the extreme property tax savings that comes with it!
